* This program compare two MPEG-2 video bitstreams
* 
* Bitstream 1 info:
* Filename (string) * /users/ytse/orig5.mpg
* Byte offset (int) * 0
* Transport bitstream? (int) * 0
* [TS?] Packet size mode (1-188 2-204) (int) @ 1
* [TS?] Video PID (int) @ 0
* 
* Bitstream 2 info:
* Filename (string) * /users/ytse/CG3/Bitstream/cp5.mpg
* Byte offset (int) * 0
* Transport bitstream? (int) * 0
* [TS?] Packet size mode (1-188 2-204) (int) @ 1
* [TS?] Video PID (int) @ 0
